              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13979251190012324878">This book left me with a melancholy and loneliness. Despite the gap between some incidents, the book was very catchy and, I could associate myself with some characters as a Turkish man who have roots from different Mediterranean countries. Reading about family members relocating to various locations, I hated once again the distance. After having finished the book, I wished I could be like a tree standing at the same point from its birth to death with other trees that I care and love. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


