<div id="review_4198923148" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4198923148" />
    <a title="James Kelly" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/89887403-james-kelly"><img alt="James Kelly" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4198923148?book_show_action=true">Aug 25, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="James Kelly" class="user" itemprop="url" name="James Kelly" href="/user/show/89887403-james-kelly">James Kelly</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781860468902" href="/book/show/232071.Ports_of_Call">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4198923148" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer514444942234339598">Better than a love story, although it is such a beautiful one. The fascination of this great book lies in the gorgeous settings encompassed in the writing, and the historical backdrop that acts as scenery and character. Lovely, graceful and generous on every subject it touches- and that is most subjects. Lovely book. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


